window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A zombie, a mimic, and a succubus walk into a bar...</b></p> <p>When Dana was killed and resurrected by a necromancer, she didn't know what to expect.</p> <p>She didn't expect to be handed a list of magical items that might cure her if she can find them.</p> <p>She definitely didn't expect the house succubus to come along to service her dangerous needs.</p> <p>And she definitely didn't expect to go head to head with an international organization dedicated to keeping magic out of human hands.</p> <p>One's dead, the other's horny. Expect the Unexpected.</p>"; 
